		Application Actions
			On SAM_AppStartup
				!
				! CHANGES, frmOrderDetails has had the problem with allocated check box fixed
						  and the sale cat data field problem fixed also.
						  on adding a order in frmOrderDetails the automatic click on pbItems has been
						  removed.
				! 15/2/95 Customer contacts and master for orchardists bug is fixed
				! 15/2/95 Deleting a customer will now check that he can be deleted and delete him
						from everywhere he needs to be leaving history though 
				! 20/2/95 Generating a credit note falling down when no of trees < no credited
				! message disabling going to orders from frmCustomer ( customer details )
				! 20/2/95 Bug in combining rods and trees in dlgQitem fixed - shouldnt combine
				! 22/2/95 custadd.apl, custcont.apl, regions.apl, frcodes.apl, regmeets.apl,
						  meetaddr.apl, pcodes.apl, custtype.apl, gcofrm.apl, barcode.apl, orddets.apl,
						  custdets.apl, nparfusl.apl, ordsload.apl where created and this program
						  is now using them.
				! 22/2/95     94 totals into customer details listing fixed
				! 23/2/95     changing order, now sets the ack_flag and Conf_flag to 'N' for one
						  on the customers orders to force acknowledgments and confirmations to print
						  out again.  Also if year is changed a order from both years orders have the 
						  ack and conf flags set to 'N'.
				! 23/2/95     frmOrderDets, frmGCOrderForm, dlgQItem, dlgCancel were commented
						  out with related internal functions as these are redundant and in future can be
						  deleted from the program to make it smaller.
				! 23/2/95    problem found with getshipaddress logic not getting a address when
						  selecting a item to order and therefore the check for prohibition fails on 
						  prohibited items.  Fixed, but should be looked at to recheck the logic in 
						  get ship address.
				! 27/2/95 Denormalising code put in - DO NOT put into live until data denormalised 
				! 27/2/95 Myfunc.apl has had the print reports and other windows taken out into
						  seperate APLs.
				! 28/2/95 Local frmOrderDetails check for not increasing conf_amt past ord_amt
						  or conf_amt < 0 like negatives not allowed messages are in place.
				! 1/3/95 region look up from postcode implemented in custdets.apl ( frmCustomer )
				! 2/3/95 various customer checks put in and stops when going to add order
				! 3/3/95 order date validation put in where checking for > current date and sequence
						of screens from frmQcustomer changed
				!
				! 3/3/95 BIG NOTE acknowledgments have changed.  a new apl replaced the
						  printack.apl called prntack2.apl.  It used a report called ACKOLD.QRP if this version
						  is going live then rename the report and the file name in the prntack2.apl
				! 15/3/95 Dont allow transfer of orders if already invoiced.  Needs testing
				! 15/3/95 Dont allow two live invoice runs.
				! 15/3/95 Update load customer invoiced flag when invoiced in this program
				! 27/4/95 Check for pulled orders in invoicing allowing for advance claims but also 
						doing the check prior to in the middle of processing orders
				!
				! 29/5/95 INVOICING SAME AS LOADS AGAIN AND POS SENDING IS ASSUMED AND NOT ASKED
				! 23/5/95 Invoicing calculate freight charges on customer basis is implemented
				! 22/11/95 Credit note fix for coral
				! Uninvoicing changes put in on 15/1/96
				!
				If strArgArray[0] = ''
					Set SqlDatabase = 'STOCKDEV'
					Set SqlUser = 'GRAHAM'
					Set SqlPassword = 'GRAHAM'
				Else
					Set SqlDatabase = strArgArray[1]
					Set SqlUser = strArgArray[2]
					Set SqlPassword = strArgArray[3]
				!
				!
				! WHEN MAKING THEN EXECUTABLE INTO STOCK CHANGE THE NAME TO CUSTOMER.EXE
				!
				! Check if program already active - TS 4/5/95
				! GF Commented these next two lines as they crash NT Machines
				! Set hWndCheckExists = FindWindowA(0,"Customer Query")
				! Set bCheckExistsWindowHidden = FALSE
				! Commented this next line of code as it crashes the program when running it.
				! If hWndCheckExists
					                                                                                                        If NOT SalIsWindowVisible( hWndCheckExists )
						                                                                                                        Set bCheckExistsWindowHidden = TRUE
					                                                                                                        Call SalBringWindowToTop( hWndCheckExists )
					! Maximize the window
					                                                                                                        Call ShowWindow(hWndCheckExists,3)
					! TS 4/5/95 Doesn't work correctly - If bCheckExistsWindowHidden
						                                                                                                                                                   Call SalHideWindow( hWndCheckExists )
					                                                                                                        Call SalMessageBeep( 1 )
					                                                                                                        Call SalQuit(  )
				!
				Call SalWaitCursor( TRUE )
				! Call SalCreateWindow( dlgLogin, hWndNULL )
				Set bShowSql = FALSE
				Set bghSqlDetail = SqlConnect( hSqlDetail )
				If bghSqlDetail
					Call SqlSetIsolationLevel( hSqlDetail, 'RL')
					Call SqlSetLockTimeout( hSqlDetail, SQLTIMEOUT )
			On SAM_SqlError
				Call SqlExtractArgs( wParam, lParam, hSqlError, nSqlError, nErrorPos )
				! Going to comments the return false line and put in others to do error processing
				! Return FALSE
				Call SqlGetErrorText( nSqlError, sErrmsg )
				Call SalNumberToStr( nSqlError, 0, sNum )
				Call SalMessageBox( sNum || '-' || sErrmsg || '.
						Choose OK to quit.', 'Customer', MB_Ok | MB_IconStop )
				! Call SalQuit(  )
				Return FALSE
			On SAM_AppExit
				If bghSqlDetail
					Call SqlDisconnect( hSqlDetail )
