						Menu Item Name:
					! Menu Item: &Rail
						                                                                                                                                                   Keyboard Accelerator: (none)
						                                                                                                                                                   Status Text: 
						                                                                                                                                                   Menu Settings 
							                                                                                                                                                   Enabled when: 
